MxNzI3YTMtN2I3ZC00NWU1LTg4ODQtNDJmZjIwYmZlZTlmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAbyAKtrODachNFzawYnwItAtvJ0tvyulsKYBakhY_cHm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fbuy-mac%2Fmac-mini" class="rapid-with-clickid">Mac Mini</a>打<a data-i13n="cpos:67;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mac-mini-review-m2-pro-2023-140052205.html">了 86 分</a>，但除了 CPU 凸起和几个额外的 Thunderbolt 端口外，这些设备几乎完全相同。</p><h2>苹果铅笔</h2><p><core-commerce id="855ffd73e7fc4e729d163baae3c25b37" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:68;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfLxQtC7rgCqJpmP1YtauUeQW8XxjdQ_lI3E0A1eIopy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07K1WWBJK%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Pencil</a>已降至 85 美元，追平了我们为 iPad 手写笔追踪的最低价格。这比该设备最近几个月的典型零售价低大约 15 美元，比苹果的厂商建议零售价低 44 美元。我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:69;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipad-accessories-130018595.html#applepencil">最佳 iPad 配件指南</a>中推荐 Pencil：对于数字艺术家和记笔记者，它是一款始终如一的准确笔，也是唯一一款在 iPadOS 上提供压力感应的手写笔。它也很容易充电和配对，因为它可以磁性连接到最新 iPad 的侧面。如果您想尝试一下，只需确保您的 iPad 与这款第二代机型<a data-i13n="cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLXVzL0hUMjExMDI5IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI2MjA2YzY1Yy02MDRjLTRiNDgtOTg4MC0yM2FmNWU3ZWY2MTcifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZ7eHRxy8yG7-lcx7a7iGgU6_0qCyG3SlUOm4tnOe0rh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT211029&amp;uuid=qtiOYPr8GOAeLVCB42364">兼容</a>。</p><h2>英特尔和 AMD CPU 交易</h2><p><core-commerce id="263c62b7190d4041b69b2721fb8aa5d4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您想要组装或升级 PC，我们会看到 Intel 和 AMD 处理器的一些优惠价格。在更好的交易中， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQlE2Q0ZEQ1g_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTA5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJiYzE3MjdhMy03YjdkLTQ1ZTUtODg4NC00MmZmMjBiZmVlOWYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXRWCQ9truoy3cT_H28Dj9_lHhtsd690vPBOyJpMLKu3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BQ6CFDCX" class="rapid-with-clickid">英特尔酷睿 i5-13500</a>降至 210 美元，比该芯片的正常价格低约 40 美元，创历史新低。对于更强大的产品， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASt2hUcAx65gYoSanqtWFZmm1bPTLjvxugFvr-q52i5G&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BQ6CSY9C%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Core i7-13700F</a>的新低价为 330 美元，比一般零售价低约 40 美元。以该价格，这在游戏和生产力方面表现出色；请注意，它缺少集成 GPU。同时，如果您更喜欢 AMD 版本， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATW_5xMG9aPOEA3iJZDCFEg0n-F2jWDwqpt904Efdu8W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BBHHT8LY%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Ryzen 7 7700X</a>可能值得一看，价格为 297 美元。它的价值<a data-i13n="cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://cpu.userbenchmark.com/Compare/Intel-Core-i7-13700F-vs-AMD-Ryzen-7-7700X/m1997481vs4131">不如</a>i7-13700F，尤其是因为<a data-i13n="cpos:75;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amd-ryzen-7000-cpu-models-leak-193730652.html">它需要</a>AM5 主板和 DDR5 RAM 才能工作，但如果您必须拥有 Ryzen PC，它仍然是游戏的可靠中档选择。</p><h2> <strong>Dashlane Premium 特卖</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="64d86bc441764d95b8206bf3db5c1a35" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>密码管理器是一种简单但有效的方法，可以<a data-i13n="cpos:76;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-26-the-best-password-managers-compared.html">提高您的在线安全性</a>并简化您需要记住的登录凭据数量。 Dashlane 是可用的更好选择之一；事实上，它很快就会成为即将发布的购买指南中的一个选择。如果您想尝试这项服务，结账时使用代码<strong>MEMDAY23</strong>或<strong>MEMORIAL23</strong>即可以 30 美元的价格获得一年的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:77;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5kcGJvbHZ3Lm5ldC9jbGljay0xMDAyMTQ4MzktMTU1MzkwODUiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImJjMTcyN2EzLTdiN2QtNDVlNS04ODg0LTQyZmYyMGJmZWU5ZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXMS3k4wOQCBFLc78HoM677ERcKjM8ISgylQ5WuKK4cV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpbolvw.net%2Fclick-100214839-15539085" class="rapid-with-clickid">Dashlane Premium</a> 。这是 50% 的折扣。尽管 Dashlane 有免费套餐，但高级计划可让您在多台设备上使用该服务。它还包括捆绑的 VPN、密码强度分析器和“暗网监控”，让您知道您的电子邮件地址是否因数据泄露而泄露。</p><h2> Paramount Plus 和 Showtime 捆绑包</h2><p><core-commerce id="43af92f60a6d49a293950ba1385071c4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>派拉蒙<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Paramount Plus;elmt:;cpos:78;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b0d3a482-802c-4eb1-9616-94f7490562f7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Paramount+Plus&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJiMGQzYTQ4Mi04MDJjLTRlYjEtOTYxNi05NGY3NDkwNTYyZjciLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucGFyYW1vdW50cGx1cy5jb20vYWNjb3VudC9zaWdudXAvcGlja3BsYW4iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImJjMTcyN2EzLTdiN2QtNDVlNS04ODg0LTQyZmYyMGJmZWU5ZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdZW6OVX9GdKgJmmUtSQy7hvDixsZld0TBPgbewIoU5Z&amp;gcRef